					br
					| Physical alarm clock coming soon!

			#request
				h3 Signup for the meaning clock!
				
				form.form.request
					.error We need all three of these guys!
					input#username(type='text', name='name', placeholder='username')				
					input#email(type='text', name='email', placeholder='your@email.com')
					input#password(type='password', name='password', placeholder='password')
